name: AVPlayerItemErrorLogEvent
desc: A single item in a player item's error log.

items.name: var date: Date?
items.desc: The date and time when the error occurred.

items.name: var uri: String?
items.desc: The URI of the playback item that had an error.

items.name: var serverAddress: String?
items.desc: The IP address of the server that was the source of the error.

items.name: var playbackSessionID: String?
items.desc: A GUID that identifies the playback session that had an error.

items.name: var errorComment: String?
items.desc: A description of the error encountered
